  05 FAC PIC 9999 VALUE ZERO.
01 V-FELDER.
  05 ERG PIC 9999 VALUE 1.
  05 I PIC 9999.
*>01 TEST-CASE-DESCRIPTIONS.
  *>05 TEST-CASE-1 PIC X(50) VALUE "a test case name".
